abstract: Toshiba Corp said on Monday it would extend the period of its tender offer for chip equipment unit NuFlare Technology Inc until Jan. 16.
snippet: Toshiba Corp said on Monday it would extend the period of its tender offer for chip equipment unit NuFlare Technology Inc until Jan. 16.
lead_paragraph: TOKYO — Toshiba Corp said on Monday it would extend the period of its tender offer for chip equipment unit NuFlare Technology Inc until Jan. 16.
headline_main: Toshiba to Extend Tender Offer Period for NuFlare Until Jan. 16
headline_print_headline: Toshiba to Extend Tender Offer Period for NuFlare Until Jan. 16

abstract: Derek Carr and the Oakland Raiders will go into the final week of the season still having a chance for the playoffs after Sunday's 24-17 victory over the Los Angeles Chargers snapped a four-game losing streak.
snippet: Derek Carr and the Oakland Raiders will go into the final week of the season still having a chance for the playoffs after Sunday's 24-17 victory over the Los Angeles Chargers snapped a four-game losing streak.
lead_paragraph: CARSON, Calif. — Derek Carr and the Oakland Raiders will go into the final week of the season still having a chance for the playoffs after Sunday's 24-17 victory over the Los Angeles Chargers snapped a four-game losing streak.
headline_main: Raiders Keep Playoff Hopes Alive With Victory Over Chargers
headline_print_headline: Raiders Keep Playoff Hopes Alive With Victory Over Chargers

abstract: It’s easy to forget those left behind in a strong economy.
snippet: It’s easy to forget those left behind in a strong economy.
lead_paragraph: In the weeks leading up to Christmas in 1975, my mother made a hard choice: Her marriage was dead and it was time to leave it.

abstract: Matt Freeman tossed in a career-high 21 points on 7-of-10 shooting and UC Santa Barbara rolled to a 68-50 victory over Merrimack on Sunday.
snippet: Matt Freeman tossed in a career-high 21 points on 7-of-10 shooting and UC Santa Barbara rolled to a 68-50 victory over Merrimack on Sunday.
lead_paragraph: SANTA BARBARA, Calif. — Matt Freeman tossed in a career-high 21 points on 7-of-10 shooting and UC Santa Barbara rolled to a 68-50 victory over Merrimack on Sunday.

lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — Cle'von Greene came off the bench to score 19 points, hitting a career-high four 3-pointers, lifting Radford to a 73-58 upset win over Richmond in the D.C. Holiday Hoopfest on Sunday.

abstract: Members of Congress should not be allowed to buy and sell stocks, or to serve on corporate boards.
snippet: Members of Congress should not be allowed to buy and sell stocks, or to serve on corporate boards.
lead_paragraph: The case of Chris Collins, the New York Republican who resigned from Congress and pleaded guilty to insider trading earlier this fall, was a rare victory in the long-running battle to ensure that members of Congress do not take improper advantage of their privileged positions.
